==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: neocolonialism
<hw>neocolonialism</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Control by a powerful country
of its former colonies (or other less developed countries) by economic
pressures. In contrast to <contr>colonialism</contr>, in which one
country controls another territory by military force.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Neocomian</ent>⟦br⟧
